            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription" ana="b1">
                <p><g type="cross-within-a-wreath"/>
                    <lb/>Εἷς, Θεός, ὁ πάντων<lb/>Δεσπότης. <choice>
                        <sic>Μνημῖον</sic>
                        <corr>Μνημεῖον</corr>
                    </choice>
                    <lb/>Μακρίνου <choice>
                        <sic>Ἀλαφάλο<lb break="no"/>υ</sic>
                        <corr>Ἀλαφάλλο<lb break="no"/>υ</corr>
                    </choice>, τελευτήσαντος με<lb break="no"/>τὰ καλοῦ ὀνόματος<lb/>καὶ καλῆς
                    πίστεως ἐτ<lb break="no"/>ῶν <num value="35">λε</num>, ἐν <choice>
                        <sic>ἔτι</sic>
                        <corr>ἔτι</corr>
                    </choice>
                    <num value="357">τνζ</num>, πε<lb break="no"/>ντεκαιδεκάτ<hi rend="ligature"
                        >ης</hi>
                    <expan><abbr>ἰνδι<lb break="no"/>κ</abbr><ex>τιῶνος</ex></expan>, ἐν μηνὶ <choice>
                        <sic>Πανέμο<lb break="no"/>υ</sic>
                        <corr>Πανήμ<lb break="no"/>ῳ</corr>
                    </choice>
                    <num value="20"><expan><abbr>εἰκοσ</abbr><ex>τῇ</ex></expan></num>, ἐν
                        ἡμέρᾳ<lb/>Κυρ<supplied reason="omitted">ι</supplied>ακῇ. Θάρσει, Μα<lb
                        break="no"/>κρῖνε, <choice><sic>οὐδὶς</sic><corr>οὐδείς</corr></choice> ἀθά<lb break="no"/>νατος.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>One (is) the God, the Lord of all. Monument of Macrinus, son of Alaphallas, who
                    died having a good name and good faith (at the age) of 35 years, in the year
                    357, in the fifteenth indiction, on the twentieth (day) of the month Panemos, on
                    Sunday. Be of good cheer, Macrinus, no one (is) immortal.</p>
            </div>
